      <intermediateExchange id="304dabd4-1703-5c5f-99b7-f5764952b4fe" unitId="2f4daad7-5331-4f14-930c-d8bca924557d" amount="0.026067255" intermediateExchangeId="0ace02fa-eca5-482d-a829-c18e46a52db4" activityLinkId="e8ef12e1-d54c-5764-8665-eca2bdeb0a94">
        <name xml:lang="en">transport, freight train</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">metric ton*km</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value, assuming average European transport distances as a proxy for Quebec. European distance derived as follows: Transport distance based on eurostat transport statistics for railway transport of goods. The transport data was extracted from the database leaf 'Railway transport &gt; Railway transport measurement - goods &gt; Goods transported by group of goods - from 2008 onwards based on NST 2007 (RAIL_GO_GRPGOOD)' (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/) on the 2023-08-02. The transport distance was calculated based on the total mass of goods transported (t) and total payload-distance (t*km) for the NST 2007 category 'GT06 - Wood and products of wood and cork (except furniture); articles of straw and plaiting materials; pulp, paper and paper products; printed matter and recorded media' in the year 2016 for all countries for which data was available. The average distance of railway transport for goods in this category in 2016 was 318 km. The fraction of goods transported by rail (in terms of mass) relative to the total mass of goods transported by road, rail and inland waterways was 8.2% in 2016. Therefore, the average distance that goods travelled by rail in 2016 was 26 km. The value is assumed to be representative for Europe.</comment>
        <uncertainty>
          <lognormal meanValue="0.026067255" mu="-3.6470753500212068" variance="0.12" varianceWithPedigreeUncertainty="0.20320000000000002"/>
          <pedigreeMatrix reliability="2" completeness="3" temporalCorrelation="5" geographicalCorrelation="5" furtherTechnologyCorrelation="4"/>
        </uncertainty>
        <property propertyId="f2283db2-62e4-467f-b9ac-c4f45be563b4" amount="0.0" isDefiningValue="false" isCalculatedAmount="false" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
